  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Dive into linear dungeons that are full of enemies and resources. Use your abilities to defeat enemies, gather resources, and get stronger every time you dive.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>Note</i></strong><i>: This is an incremental, linear progression game. Not a roguelike. There are no randomized builds or multiple playstyles. Your journey is centered on consistent growth, unlocking new upgrades, and getting stronger over time.</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2572300/extras/5cd13d245709fc7ab0046bbbcb796b01.poster.avif?t=1771255066\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2572300/extras/5cd13d245709fc7ab0046bbbcb796b01.webm?t=1771255066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2572300/extras/5cd13d245709fc7ab0046bbbcb796b01.mp4?t=1771255066\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the upgrade skill tree to become stronger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2572300/extras/1386bb0796b6d016e8fcb3c4c111def0.poster.avif?t=1771255066\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2572300/extras/1386bb0796b6d016e8fcb3c4c111def0.webm?t=1771255066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2572300/extras/1386bb0796b6d016e8fcb3c4c111def0.mp4?t=1771255066\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master every skill to become the god of the row!</p><p c